Hi guyss, I’m back with another empties video. Let’s get right into it 🥰

@nichebeautylab Azelaic Acid Serum (PR): One of the  best azelaic acid products I’ve ever used. It contains 15% azelaic acid, ceramides, colloidal oatmeal and glycerin. This product calms the skin, fights mild-moderate acne, and fades hyperpigmentation (when used alongside other tyrosinase inhibitors). 

@goodal_official Vegan Rice Milk Toner: A no-fuss hydrating product that works well with other skincare products. I bought this because of the size (250ml is a winner). Notable ingredients include vegan rice milk, aqua ceramide, panthenol and chlorella vulgaris extract. I prefer viscous toners so I certainly enjoyed this one. I just wish the hydration lasted a little longer. The brand describes it as a moisturising toner but I didn’t find it moisturising. 

@theinkeylist Salicylic Acid Cleanser: If you’re looking for an affordable cleanser that tackles blackheads & whiteheads, look no further. This cleanser is so gentle and non-stripping, I used it 1-2 times a day without any issues. It contains 2% BHA, zinc, and allantoin. 

@beautyofjoseon_official Glow Serum: I had high expectations for this product and I’m glad I wasn’t disappointed! This has a viscous consistency and truly adds a nice glow to the skin. It is soothing, anti-inflammatory and non-sticky. It contains 60% propolis extract and 2% niacinamide so I use it as an anti-oxidant serum. I couldn’t give it 10/10 because I wish it came in a bigger size.

@nichebeautylab Pure Glycerin Serum (PR): Now this is a hydrating product that is equally moisturising. This serum is deeply hydrating and leaves my skin feeling smooth and plump. It is formulated with 15% glycerin and 5% amino acid complex. It feels elegant and leaves no sticky finish. Get this if you want long-lasting hydration!

@sosserum Night Cream (PR): This gem has become one of fave moisturisers. I love how it absorbs into my skin within seconds. This moisturiser supports moisture retention and served me well during the colder months. It contains red algae sea moss, cranberry and hyaluronic acid.

