@coola Scalp & Hair Mist SPF30 $28

@sunbum Scalp & Hair Mist SPF30 $17.49

Same user experience. Both use chemical UV filters, are CF + Vegan, are hair colour-safe while the Coola claims to also protect colour fading from the sun. The Sun Bum also has that drugstore sunscreen coconut scent which people love or hate 💋

